                          </span>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="display: none;" class="fact">
                        <td class="fact">
                          <p>
                            Zendo will make you a more efficient learner in a few ways. First, by using flashcards and answering questions, you are testing yourself. Repeated testing is at the heart of effective learning. Zendo also helps you sort through what really matters and study only what you have forgotten. Zendo does this by estimating importance based on how often you review a card, and what you got for a score (self-graded).
                          </p>
                        </td>
